            <title>[SPR-6353] TestContext framework should support one AspectJ instance per ApplicationContext</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6353</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;TheSymptom&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;The Symptom&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Each test passes when running individually;&lt;/li&gt;
